[gd_scene load_steps=7 format=3 uid="uid://calimahistart1"]

; Historical artifact — gold / historically-significant pieces (museum-bound). Open this
; scene to change the model and to add/move/remove ArtifactConditionDecal children (each
; is a condition; the texture file name decides type + cleaning tool). "Randomized Decal
; Count" on the root picks how many of the placed conditions appear per run (re-rolled
; each loop / new save). 0 = always show them all.

